code: @ConditionalOnBean(LoadBalancerClient.class) @ConditionalOnMissingBean @Bean("netflix-client-load-balancer-adapter") public CamelSpringCloudServiceLoadBalancer.LoadBalancerClientAdapter netflixClientLoadBalancerAdapter(List<ConversionService> conversionServices) {     return client -> new CamelCloudNetflixServiceLoadBalancer(client, conversionServices). }
